genresAdvancedInfo.name: goa psytrance
genresAdvancedInfo.description: With roots in the Goa region of India, this subgenre of trance music is known for its psychedelic and trippy sound. The use of complex rhythms, distorted synths, and heavy basslines create a mind-bending experience, perfect for festivals and raves. The music often incorporates elements of Hinduism and Eastern spirituality.
